        <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">Non Domesticated Animals</skos:prefLabel>
        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">Any animal other than livestock (animals carried as food); animals used for transport (horses; mules); and domestic pets. Such animals may be exported as specimens, for zoos, menageries, and circuses, or as unusual pets (e.g. elephants, monkeys).</skos:scopeNote>
      </skos:Concept>
